    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1176553/" class="title-link">【读品•品评】范昀：以理性解读疯狂</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1176553"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dupin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1197515-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dupin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">【读品】</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-07-06"
      class="main-meta">2007-07-06 11:19:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1176553_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  翻看《德国反犹史》，不免想到那个论争了千百回的问题：纳粹为何要对犹太赶尽杀绝？这场人类历史上空前绝后惨绝人寰的大屠杀，几乎是一场梦魇，启蒙理想遭受重创，文明世界颜面扫地，历史虚无主义则在深处发端，滋生蔓延。 这是不容回避的疑问，然而这一问题的解释却未必如想象...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1176553/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
